main event: On 10 July 1958, two objects were observed over the air force base in Udine, Italy.
interesting points: The sighting occurred at 5:30 p.m.,Witnesses included Signor Bartolo Salvatore and other civilian personnel,The observation involved two unidentified flying objects,The Air Force's investigation into the incident remains inconclusive,The documentation reflects ongoing inquiries about UFO sightings during the late 1950s.
